              "code": "66",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "样例说明",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "$\\hspace{15pt}$对于第一组测试数据，$s = \\texttt{aba}$，有两种可行分割方案：",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "$\\hspace{23pt}\\bullet\\,$拆分为 $\\texttt{a}$、$\\texttt{b}$、$\\texttt{a}$，价值 $1^2 + 1^2 + 1^2 = 3$；",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "$\\hspace{23pt}\\bullet\\,$保持原状，价值 $3^2 = 9$。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "$\\hspace{15pt}$对于第二组测试数据，$s = \\texttt{ab}$，唯一可行方案为拆分为：",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "$\\hspace{23pt}\\bullet\\,$$\\texttt{a}$、$\\texttt{b}$，价值 $1^2 + 1^2 = 2$。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "$\\hspace{15pt}$对于第三组测试数据，$s = \\texttt{aaaa}$，任意子串均为回文串，所有分割方案对应将 $4$ 分拆为有序正整数和：",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "$\\hspace{23pt}\\bullet\\,$$1+1+1+1$：价值 $1+1+1+1 = 4$；",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "$\\hspace{23pt}\\bullet\\,$$1+1+2$：价值 $1+1+4 = 6$；",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "$\\hspace{23pt}\\bullet\\,$$1+2+1$：价值 $1+4+1 = 6$；",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "$\\hspace{23pt}\\bullet\\,$$2+1+1$：价值 $4+1+1 = 6$；",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "$\\hspace{23pt}\\bullet\\,$$1+3$：价值 $1+9 = 10$；",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "$\\hspace{23pt}\\bullet\\,$$3+1$：价值 $9+1 = 10$；",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "$\\hspace{23pt}\\bullet\\,$$2+2$：价值 $4+4 = 8$；",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "$\\hspace{23pt}\\bullet\\,$$4$：价值 $16$。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "$\\hspace{15pt}$总和为 $4+6+6+6+10+10+8+16 = 66$。",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
