    {
      "heading": "题解",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "先用区间 dp 的方法把回文数组<code>hui</code>预处理出来，然后考虑 $O(N^2)$ 的枚举。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "基于划分型 dp，把序列分成 <code>[其它段][回文段]</code>，考虑枚举 $s(j, i)$。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "当 $s(j, i)$ 是回文串时，再进行转移，这样保证不会算重，因为 $s[i]$ 在前面的 dp 没出现过。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "也得算一下 $f[i]$ 表示前面的分割方案数。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "转移方程：$dp[i] = s(j,i)的权值  * f[j - 1] + dp[j - 1]$",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "void solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tint n; cin >> n;\n\tstring s; cin >> s; s = ' ' + s;\n\tvar dp = vector<ll>(n + 1);\n\tvar f = vector<ll>(n + 1);\n\tvar hui = Vec2<bool>(n + 1, n + 1);\n\tfa(i, 1, n)hui[i][i] = hui[i][i - 1] = 1;\n\tfa(len, 2, n)fa(i, 1, n) {\n\t\tint j = i + len - 1;\n\t\tif (j > n)break;\n\t\tif (hui[i + 1][j - 1] and s[i] == s[j]) {\n\t\t\thui[i][j] = 1;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\tf[0] = 1;\n\tfa(i, 1, n) {\n\t\tfb(j, i, 1) {\n\t\t\tif (hui[j][i]) {\n\t\t\t\tll now = (i - j + 1) * (i - j + 1);\n\t\t\t\tf[i] = (f[i] + f[j - 1]) % mod;\n\t\t\t\tdp[i] = (dp[i] + now * f[j - 1] % mod + dp[j - 1]) % mod;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\tcout << dp[n] << endl;\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
